					<description><![CDATA[<p>Candid Health Raises Fresh Capital To Modernise Healthcare Billing Artificial intelligence health startup Candid Health has secured $120 million in Series D financing led by Sixth Street Growth with other</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/candid-health-raises-120m-ai-revenue-cycle-management/" data-wpel-link="internal">Candid Health Raises $120M to Expand AI-Powered Healthcare Revenue Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2><b>Candid Health Raises Fresh Capital To Modernise Healthcare Billing</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Artificial intelligence health startup Candid Health has secured $120 million in Series D financing led by Sixth Street Growth with other participants include Oak HC/FT, 8VC and Y Combinator to bring artificial intelligence into healthcare’s revenue cycle management (RCM). </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The latest funding puts the company three times more expensive than its last round, a Series C in February 2025. It will fuel its efforts to build the infrastructure for the financial services underpinning America’s health system by upgrading legacy billing processes and introducing automation based on artificial intelligence. </span></p>
<h2><b>AI Platform Replaces Outdated Billing Systems</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company rebuilt the underlying infrastructure to enable automation throughout the entire billing process. Its highly configurable rules engine, coupled with AI workflows that learn and evolve over time, proactively identifies routine administrative activities and cuts back on associated administrative hours. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">CEO and co-founder Nick Perry explains that for years, the healthcare industry has been saddled with legacy billing solutions that have been unable to cope with increasingly complex provider organizations. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">We completely rebuilt the foundation of our company and our financial infrastructure from the ground up, said Perry. This allows us to drive major cost savings for our customers and also increase their revenue collection by taking the burden off administrative and finance teams through automated workflows.</span></p>
<h2><b>Enterprise Demand Fuels Rapid Growth</b></h2>
<div id="attachment_203709" style="width: 1322px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-203709" class="size-full wp-image-203709" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/07/Candid-3.png" alt="Illustration of an AI-powered healthcare revenue cycle platform automating medical billing, financial workflows, and administrative operations across hospitals and healthcare providers." width="1312" height="736" /><p id="caption-attachment-203709" class="wp-caption-text">Growing enterprise adoption of agentic AI is transforming healthcare revenue cycle management, enabling providers to automate complex administrative processes, improve financial performance, and devote more time to patient care. Source: Created by Ventureburn.</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Candid Health is currently employed by over 200 organizations ranging across more than dozens of medical sub-specialties and represents many of the nation&#8217;s largest and most rapid growing healthcare providers. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company generated 190 percent year-over-year annual contracted run rate revenue growth, alongside a 180 percent net dollar retention in 2025, illustrating customer adoption with enterprises. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">“Revenue cycle management continues to be one of the most daunting operational issues the healthcare sector faces as it directly impacts providers, patients, and ultimately, the entire ecosystem of healthcare,” said co-founder and Chief Operating Officer Doug Proctor in a prepared statement.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The emergence of agentic AI allows healthcare organizations to automate some of the most complicated billing procedures, so providers can spend more time focused on care and less time managing administration.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The importance of customer delight was among another one of the reasons noted by investors for providing funding. Sixth Street Growth said discussions with nearly 40 customers consistently demonstrated meaningful improvements in operational efficiency and financial performance after adopting the platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News: </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/arrakis-raises-38m-to-scale-ai-deployment-for-industrial-operations/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">Arrakis Raises $38M to Scale AI Deployment for Industrial Operations</span></a></p>
<h2><b>Funding Will Strengthen Healthcare Financial Infrastructure</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The new investment will help Candid Health continue expanding its AI platform while supporting growing demand from enterprise healthcare providers across the United States. Reimbursement for America’s medical services industry costs providers $280 billion annually.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The company aims to further automate healthcare reimbursement processes by reducing manual intervention, improving collections, and lowering administrative costs for medical organisations.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">As healthcare providers increasingly seek technology that improves financial performance without adding operational complexity, AI-powered revenue cycle management platforms are attracting growing investor interest.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">With strong </span><a href="https://www.investopedia.com/terms/r/revenue.asp" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">revenue</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> growth, expanding enterprise adoption, and fresh capital, Candid Health is positioning itself to become a core financial infrastructure provider for the next generation of healthcare organisations.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">To stay updated on crypto venture capital funding and market trends, visit our </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/category/news/venture-capital/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">venture capital news section</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> for more insights.</span></p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/candid-health-raises-120m-ai-revenue-cycle-management/" data-wpel-link="internal">Candid Health Raises $120M to Expand AI-Powered Healthcare Revenue Platform</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
