										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><b>Launched in October 2022</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Decentrawood is an AI-powered Web3 entertainment ecosystem that combines gaming, intelligent AI, the metaverse, social experiences, and digital ownership into a unified platform. With the launch of </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the ecosystem has expanded to enable users to create, verify, deploy, and use autonomous AI agents for real-world automation and personalized digital experiences. Powered by the </span><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> token, Decentrawood continues to expand its ecosystem by integrating AI, blockchain technology, and Web3 entertainment into a single decentralized platform. </span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The project is also rapidly expanding its exchange presence, with </span><b>DEOD set to list on BingX on August 7, 2026</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, while consistently securing new exchange listings almost every month to improve accessibility and liquidity for its growing global community. </span></p>
<h2><b>What is Decentrawood?</b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Decentrawood is an AI-powered Web3 entertainment ecosystem designed to redefine how people play, create, connect, and earn in the digital world. Built on blockchain technology, it brings together immersive gaming, autonomous AI, the metaverse, social experiences, a decentralized marketplace, and token-powered rewards into one seamless platform.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">At the heart of the ecosystem is </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, enabling users to create, verify, deploy, and use intelligent AI agents for real-world automation and personalized digital experiences. Whether you&#8217;re a gamer, creator, developer, or Web3 enthusiast, Decentrawood provides the tools and infrastructure to explore the future of decentralized entertainment.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Powered by the </span><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> token, every interaction across the ecosystem unlocks new opportunities—from playing games and staking tokens to using AI agents, trading digital assets, and participating in community-driven experiences. Decentrawood is building a future where entertainment, artificial intelligence, and blockchain work together to create a smarter, more rewarding digital economy.</span></p>
