<p><b>DEOD</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is one of those projects. With the successful launch of </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, Decentrawood has expanded from a Web3 entertainment platform into an </span><b>Agentic AI ecosystem</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, allowing users to create, verify, deploy, and monetize AI agents.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Combined with </span><b>live staking, multiple exchange listings, and a growing community</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, DEOD continues to strengthen its ecosystem. These developments could support long-term growth as AI and Web3 remain two of the fastest-growing sectors in crypto.</span></p>
