<h3><b>Token Utility</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The DEOD token acts as the core utility asset across the Decentrawood ecosystem. It is used for staking, accessing platform features, participating in ecosystem activities, supporting governance, and powering in-game and creator economies. As more users engage with the ecosystem and new products launch, demand for the token could grow alongside platform adoption.</span></p>
<h3><b>Long-Term Outlook</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DEOD&#8217;s investment case is supported by continuous ecosystem development rather than speculation alone. The combination of a structured token economy, expanding AI capabilities, blockchain gaming, active staking, and ongoing exchange growth provides several long-term catalysts. As the project continues executing its roadmap, DEOD is well positioned to benefit from increasing adoption of both AI and Web3 technologies.</span></p>
<h2><b>DEOD Technical Analysis</b></h2>
