<h3><b>Price History</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">DEOD has been one of the stronger-performing AI-focused Web3 tokens in recent months. Over the last </span><b>30 days</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the token has gained </span><b>97.3%</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, while posting </span><b>41.8%</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> growth in the past </span><b>14 days</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and </span><b>19%</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> over the last </span><b>7 days</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, reflecting sustained buying momentum despite broader market volatility. Currently trading around </span><b>$0.018</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, DEOD is only about </span><b>80% away from reclaiming its previous all-time high of $0.024</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, making it one of the few projects approaching a major breakout level instead of recovering from deep losses.</span></p>
