<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Several strong catalysts continue to support DEOD&#8217;s long-term outlook. The project recently launched </span><b>DEOD AI</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, expanding the ecosystem into the rapidly growing AI sector. At the same time, exchange adoption continues to accelerate. </span><b>WEEX</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> and </span><b>CoinDCX Web3</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> were added in July, while </span><b>BingX</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> is scheduled to list DEOD on </span><b>7 August</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">, continuing the team&#8217;s strategy of adding new exchanges almost every month. Combined with staking, ecosystem expansion, and increasing visibility, these developments could provide additional momentum if buying pressure continues.</span></p>
